@qsaerts
hey man, i had the same problem, this is the fix:
go to the folder that has the redistributibles .exe files, on my win 8 64 bit system it was here: C:Program Files (x86)Bethesda SoftworksDishonoredBinariesRedist and choose the packages appropriate to your system, i used the 64 bit options (obviously) hope this helped:)

